{"id":1688042,"retrievedAt":"2026-05-05T12:22:56.630Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[{"id":16,"name":"Animation"}],"homepage":"","id":1688042,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"The Great Diamond: Long Division","overview":"In the kingdom of Boravia, a war erupted between the Waggles and the Dros after the discovery of a massive diamond. Initially living in harmony, their relationship soured when the diamond became a point of contention. The Dros, determined to keep the diamond, cut it into smaller gems to hide them from the Waggles. After a prolonged conflict, the Waggles captured the Dros' fortress but found the diamond missing. The Dros had successfully smuggled the smaller gems away. Eventually, both sides agreed to peace and divided the gems among their families, leaving one stone to symbolize their shared history of greed and conflict.","popularity":0.0357,"poster_path":null,"production_companies":[{"id":160939,"logo_path":null,"name":"Davidson Films","origin_country":""},{"id":60287,"logo_path":null,"name":"Encyclopædia Britannica Films","origin_country":"US"}],"production_countries":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","name":"United States of America"}],"release_date":"1975-12-12","revenue":0,"runtime":10,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"The Great Diamond: Long Division","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"Great Diamond: Long Division","type":""},{"iso_3166_1":"US","title":"Math That Counts","type":""}]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1802779,"known_for_department":"Sound","name":"Peter J. Smith","original_name":"Peter J. Smith","popularity":0.0071,"profile_path":null,"cast_id":3,"character":"","credit_id":"69f8ba0b947a429b4f338145","order":0}],"crew":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":3234426,"known_for_department":"Writing","name